com.gams.api

Class GAMSGlobals

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gams.api.GAMSGlobals

  • public class GAMSGlobals
extends java.lang.Object
    GAMSGlobals defines constants that are used by com.gams.api package. These constants include equation subtype, variable subtype, solver termination conditions, model solution status, and update action.
